text: Tumi tata ketiya'o chalatara babe thiya nahaâ€™ba; yi machajidara bhitti prathama dinara paraa'i sthapita haiche takbaraara oparata, se'itotahe chalatara babe thiya horaa tomara babe bechi upayukta. Tata enekuraa loka ache yisakale uttamaraupe paraitrata arjana karaa bhalapaya, arau paraitrata arjanakaraisakalaka allahe bhalapaya
